extendedInfo.description: Display all startup app(user & system).Manage Startup app(Detail/Uninstall/Find in market).Improve your phone start speed!Very easy to use.support android 1.5 and up.KW: startup manager boot up app cleaner system app memory.V2.1:Big change!Any problem or suggestion please EMAIL me!

reviews.title: Love it !  Unrooted phone.
reviews.comment: Just what I was looking for.   Stopped all my downloaded apps from loading at startup. Thanks!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Simple & straightforward solution
reviews.comment: It does exactly what is designed to do without using up all of your memory. I would love to see more features ie. Process manager, system info & or cache/history cleanup, etc. Other than that, it gets the job done & I\'m well pleased. #kudos
